      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，Idle到Loading的触发条件是Start Request。那从Success和Error之后，用户怎么回到初始状态？还有，Error状态有没有终止流程的出口？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Success",
        "Error",
        "Idle",
        "Reset",
        "Retry",
        "Abort"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Success之后用户可以选择Reset回到Idle；Error的话有两个选择，Retry回到Idle重试，或者Abort直接结束整个流程。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Success",
        "Reset",
        "Idle",
        "Error",
        "Retry",
        "Abort"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我用stateDiagram-v2来画。起点指向Idle，然后Loading分支到Success和Error，Error这里我画两条出线，一条Retry回Idle，一条Abort到终点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "[*]",
        "Idle",
        "Loading",
        "Success",
        "Error",
        "Retry",
        "Abort"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "等下，Abort那条线确认是走到终态吗？不是回到Idle？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Error",
        "Abort",
        "[*]"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的，Abort是直接结束，用[*]表示终态。Retry才是回到Idle。这两个我分开画了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Error",
        "Abort",
